      <h3>
        <img src="/assets/img/logo-lcm2.svg" alt="#LoveCintaMahabbah">
      </h3>

      <p class="i18n lang--en">
        "Our latest album titled <em>#LoveCintaMahabbah</em> is special to us first because
        we feel that we didn't leave anything behind&hellip; meaning, we brought all our past,
        the good, the not-so-good&hellip; all of it with us! But if you ask me, the sweetness
        of our latest album lies in between the tracks&hellip; literally and figuratively
        speaking," said Erwan.
      </p>
      <p class="i18n lang--ms">
        “Album terbaru kami mempunyai pendekatan yang unik kerana ia tampil dengan
        variasi lagu yang inshaa Allah boleh diterima oleh semua golongan dalam setiap
        peringkat usia. Ia lebih segar, catchy dan mesej lagu dapat difahami dengan mudah.
        Kami juga akan menyanyikan sebuah qasidah yang umurnya beratus tahun karangan
        ulama’ terdahulu iaitu <em>Habib Abdullah bin Alwi AlHaddad</em> berjudul <em>‘Qod Kafani’</em>.”
      </p>

      <p class="i18n lang--en">
        "Not leaving anything behind is one thing&hellip; we've also tried to put in our
        present as much as we could. Many of our friends from the music side and also a dear
        friend from the academic side didn't hesitate to respond to our invitation to be
        featured in our latest album," said Adib.
      </p>
      <p class="i18n lang--ms">
        Album ini juga akan menampilkan beberapa orang artis sebagai penampilan istimewa
        untuk beberapa buah lagu antaranya Zain Hamid, Taj Addin, Ramli Mohar, Ahmad
        Izham Omar dan Syech Radzie Mawladdawillah.
      </p>

      <p class="i18n lang--en">
        And both Erwan and Adib agree that, although now they are not as young in age as before,
        but this chapter of their journey has just begun&hellip; and they hope to invite as many
        as possible to come and join them! InsyaAllah.
      </p>
      <p class="i18n lang--ms">
        The Muhibbain teruja dengan penghasilan buah tangan terbaharu ini, Segalanya
        baharu! Daripada kehadiran tahun baharu, pertambahan anggota, label dan dapat
        bekerjasama dengan mereka yang berpengalaman. Mereka mengharapkan album
        dan mesej di dalamnya diterima oleh semua sebagaimana matlamat asal, InsyaAllah.
      </p>

      <hr>

